Pitch manipulation through SSML was tested with MaryTTS. Test sentences were 
synthesized with all three voices, seven different target pitch values and at 
three different speech rates. For each configuration, all sentences in the 
"syllable_count_corpus.txt" file in the "misc" folder were synthesized. Actual
pitch values were measured with Praat.

These are the results:
rate modifier: -30%
target    cmu-bdl-hsmm    cmu-rms-hsmm    cmu-slt-hsmm
100       101.5 (1.6)      99.2 (1.5)      99.5 (1.2)
110       111.1 (1.6)     108.6 (1.6)     109.1 (1.1)
120       120.8 (1.6)     117.9 (1.7)     119.1 (1.3)
130       130.7 (1.5)     127.7 (1.6)     129.2 (1.4)
140       140.6 (1.9)     137.6 (1.6)     139.2 (1.2)
150       150.1 (1.7)     147.5 (1.6)     149.1 (1.3)
160       159.6 (1.6)     157.5 (1.6)     158.9 (1.1)
default                                   170.5 (2.1)

rate modifier: +0%
target    cmu-bdl-hsmm    cmu-rms-hsmm    cmu-slt-hsmm
default   119.9 (1.7)      94.2 (1.4)     170.1 (2.0)
100       101.3 (1.7)      99.1 (1.7)      99.3 (1.4)
110       110.8 (1.7)     108.3 (1.6)     108.7 (1.2)
120                                       119.1 (1.6)
130       130.4 (1.6)     127.4 (1.6)     130.3 (2.7)
140       140.3 (2.0)     137.3 (1.7)     139.8 (2.0)
150       149.8 (1.7)     147.3 (1.6)     149.2 (1.7)
160       159.3 (1.5)     157.2 (1.6)     158.8 (1.4)

rate modifier: +30%
target    cmu-bdl-hsmm    cmu-rms-hsmm    cmu-slt-hsmm
default                                   170.2 (2.3)
100       101.7 (2.3)      98.9 (1.7)      99.6 (1.7)
110       111.3 (2.2)     108.2 (1.6)     109.2 (1.8)
120       120.9 (2.0)     117.5 (1.7)     120.6 (2.9)
130       130.4 (1.7)     127.3 (1.6)     134.3 (4.5)
140       140.2 (1.7)     137.3 (1.6)     143.9 (4.5)
150       149.7 (1.8)     147.2 (1.6)     151.2 (3.3)
160       159.2 (1.6)     157.2 (1.6)     159.5 (2.2)

In summary, the pitch manipulation is accurate within about 4Hz on average 
(greatest delta about 4.3Hz).

